ies, and that these agricultural activities themselves were not an important source of mercury. We conclude bats did not demonstrate a signature of mercury risk either as a result of proximity of gold mining, or as a result of agricultural activities.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Carrasco-Rueda, Farah", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Loiselle, Bette A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Frederick, Peter C.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/878eae4f5023802d8b1f1e157ff75afa", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/08a94eb79192a8e7757843c543e09bc274e4d850d8f163e733eb709884819747", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/EN9KD8JH", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/EN9KD8JH", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/c6de1e945e7a394f14651800fda43473!/b176528-179015", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "7", "pages": "1032-1042", "title": "Ecotoxicology", "volume": "29"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/878eae4f5023802d8b1f1e157ff75afa"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:EN9KD8JH"}, {"identifier": "10.1007/s10646-020-02195-3"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations